text: Ærest of strætforda up andlang þæs grenan weges to smiceran æc; andlang wegges to Ketanlege upewerdre; andlang herpaðes to þam herpaþes on norð healfe lobirihtes gete.
Of þam herpaðe benorþan labirihtes gete on ðære dice hyrnan adune on þære land sceare to þam twam wicon adune andlanges drianhyrstes lace.
Fram ðære lace to þam ligcgendum æc; fram ðam licgendum æc innan sticelan ford; of ðam forda andlang herpaðes of wulfrices dice hyrnan.
Fram þære dice hyrnan andlang hæccean to bridianbeara lace on þone hnottan stybb; of þam hnottan stybbe andlang hæccean on ðone mycclan mapeldran.
Andlang hæccean to þære ræw apoldran; andlang hæccean to cern hlinces herpaðe.
Andlang herpaðes to þan holan wege; andlang dic suð to þære holan lace; andlang ðære lace up innan þone herpað; andlang herpaþes innan hweouforda.
